name: Last Story In December
description:
A blessing for those who can read this for more than 2 years we have survived the pandemic together. 
There are so many sad stories that we have written and other people have written. 
Everything is getting better and better and hope to return to normal again. 
In December we will end the story for the year. 
We are too busy to think about new resolutions in the new year, until we forget to end the story in this chapter well. 
let's thank each other and end this story with the best version of each of us.
Thank You

Digital Illustration
7000 x 7000 PX
